	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Salutem in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Dominus diriget/dirigat corda Civitatum, quo nihil adprobent, quam quod consonum sit verbo domini puro.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Varii sparguntur rumores de missa papist[ic]a invehenda in nostras Civitates.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Sunt varię practicę a Caesareanis; verum dominus absque dubio dissipabit eas, si nos veram pęnitentiam egerimus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Quid <placeName ref="l491">Argentinę</placeName> agatur, in ista scheda inclusa invenies, dein quid in <placeName ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName>; quas schedas cupio remitti cum tua oratione, quam habuisti contra Interim, et si quid praeterea habes, quod contra Interim ab aliis sit scriptum, oro, velis communicare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Senatus noster ea, quae propositurus est paganis, nobis praelegit; nos non potuimus ea comprobare.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">De hac re alias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Raptim, <placeName ref="l28">Basileę</placeName> 1548. 28. Novembris in ipso prandio.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">D. <persName ref="p8171">Theodorum</persName>, <persName ref="p8127">Pellicanum</persName> et <persName ref="p7228">[Zving]lium</persName> nomine meo salutabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Tuus <persName ref="p1278">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" ana="salute"><persName ref="p467">Bucerus</persName> vos omnes salutat in domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de">Man sagt, der <persName ref="p7736">von Rosenberg</persName> und der <persName ref="p8034">von Heideg</persName> seyen in kaiserlicher ach, item der von <placeName ref="l3562">Büchlingen</placeName>, der graff sey <foreign xml:lang="la">deprehensus in adultero</foreign> und erschossen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de">Der keyser soll hefftig kranck sin, das mann in müsse ätzen; <foreign xml:lang="la">nunquam ita periculose laboravit.</foreign></s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Id a quodam nobili <placeName ref="l1273">Ensesheimensi</placeName> audivi, qui ex Buxlla ad nos venit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de">Diser brieff gehört dem wolgelerten herren meyster <persName ref="p495">Heinrich Bullinger</persName>, lütpriester zuͦ <placeName ref="l587">Zurich</placeName>, mynem gunstigen herren zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de"><placeName ref="l587">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
